data.description: * 1/2 acre Lot* Space for your Toys & More! Come see this Turn Key, Completely Remolded, Multi-Level Beauty*From the street you will fall in love the curb appeal as brick paver walk way lead to home* Pardo offers everything NEW* Exterior Doors (2022), Newer Windows*New Roof  (2023)*New Boiler w/ Transferrable Warranty (2023)*New Laminate flooring throughout, Updated  Eat-In Kitchen w/ Corian countertops, New Appliances*Light Fixtures, New Interior Doors w/hardware, both baths have been remodeled and/or updated*Updated Electrical and Plumbing*Nice size laundry room*Walk outside to find the detached 2.5 car garage*lighted patio for entertaining and a huge backyard that is fully fenced*Beautiful exterior landscaping and lighting*Additional parking pad for your boat, trailer, toys and more* Appliances (2022) are negotiable*B.A.T.V.A.I* Make your appointment today before this beauty is GONE**Showings begin Sunday, Feb 25th**
